high_descs: Turn right, walk past the coffee table, then turn right and go to the chair on your left.
Pick up the keys on the chair.
Turn right and go to the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Look at keys using the lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the table, and then turn right towards the left chair in front of you.
Pick up the set of keys on the chair.
Turn right towards the lamp at the corner of the room.
anns.task_desc: Examine a set of keys at the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Move to the opposite side of the room to the far left tan chair that the keys are sitting on top of
Pick up the keys that are on top of the chair
Carry the keys across the room to the large floor lamp
anns.task_desc: Carry keys while turning on a lamp
